item.title: By: Stacey
item.dc:creator: Stacey
item.description: Nice image! I'll go see the new one, but I plan to wait. We got so excited for episode 1 that we went the day it was released. So sad. So very sad. Saw #2, but not quite as soon. May wait a while this time. Trying not to get my hopes up. Low expectations might help.
